{"key":"post-13960023","value":"<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<post>\n<id>13960023</id>\n<content>Fractional sterilization is going to fail with rye more often than it succeeds.&amp;nbsp; I have however, found a better way to sterilize grains without a pressure cooker.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;First, soak and boil your grains as shown in the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mushroomvideos.com/Grain-Preparation&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer noopener&quot;&gt;five steps to grain preparation&lt;/a&gt;, and then load your hydrated grains into jars with filtered lids.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Next, boil/steam them ala brf tek for 8 hours.&amp;nbsp; Don't start counting the 8 hours until steam is escaping from under the lid of your pot.&amp;nbsp; Add small amounts of hot water as necessary during the steaming process to prevent your pot from boiling dry.&amp;nbsp; A second pot used to pre-boil the water really helps here.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Once they're done, cool and inoculate.&amp;nbsp; I've had 100% success with this method over the last year in my &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mushroomvideos.com/55-Gallon-Drum-Sterilizer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer noopener&quot;&gt;55 gallon drum sterilizer&lt;/a&gt; which will sterilize 100 pounds of grain or supplemented sawdust per cycle.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I've never much cared for beef cooked in a pressure cooker because it tends to get rubbery and slimy.&amp;nbsp; However, it's the shit for lobster.&amp;nbsp; Cook for five minutes at 5 psi, and then strip the shell off, roll in butter and place on the BBQ grill for a few minutes until the surface of the lobster begins to toast.&amp;nbsp; Damn, makes me want to rob a bank so I can afford a 2 pound rock lobster tail in this economy. &lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/smileys/rolleyes.gif&quot; alt=&quot;:rolleyes:&quot; title=&quot;:rolleyes:&quot;/&gt;&lt;br /&gt;RR&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://files.shroomery.org/files/07-009/259775434-Lobster_night_1a.jpg&quot; class=&quot;highslide&quot; onclick=&quot;return hs.expand(this,{slideshowGroup:'hsg1'})&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width:192px;height:auto;&quot; src=&quot;/forums/thumbs/07-009/259775434-thumb_Lobster_night_1a.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>13960039</next>\n<prev>13959832</prev>\n<first>13959463</first>\n<last>14348547</last>\n<when>1297696796</when>\n<utime>02/14/11 05:19 PM</utime>\n</post>"}